    <title>Hexo Markdown</title>
    <link href="/2025/01/28/Markdown/"/>
    <url>/2025/01/28/Markdown/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo-Markdown语法"><a href="#Hexo-Markdown语法" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Markdown语法"></a>Hexo Markdown语法</h1><h2 id="文章格式"><a href="#文章格式" class="headerlink" title="文章格式"></a>文章格式</h2><p>‘front-matter’的基本格式示例如下：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><figcaption><span>[title] [lang:language] [url] [link text] [additional options]</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span>  <span class="hljs-string">Hexo</span> <span class="hljs-string">Markdown</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">date:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2025-01-28 14:52:16</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">tags:</span> [<span class="hljs-string">Markdown</span>, <span class="hljs-string">Latex</span>]<br><span class="hljs-attr">categories:</span> <span class="hljs-string">学习</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">toc:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">mathjax:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="斜体和粗体"><a href="#斜体和粗体" class="headerlink" title="斜体和粗体"></a>斜体和粗体</h2><p>使用<span class="label label-primary">*和**</span>表示粗体和斜体</p><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><figcaption><span>[title] [lang:language] [url] [link text] [additional options]</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc"><span class="hljs-strong">*斜体*</span>， <span class="hljs-strong">**粗体**</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果：这是<em>斜体</em>，这是<strong>粗体</strong>。</p><h2 id="分级标题"><a href="#分级标题" class="headerlink" title="分级标题"></a>分级标题</h2><p>使用’&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>]]></content>
    
    
